              <h3 class="invis">Author bio</h3>
                                                                                              <a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/jack-tamisiea/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_bottom" >
                      <div class="container col3 ">
                        <div class="col span2"><p>Jack Tamisiea is a science writer based in Washington, DC. He loves searching for new stories in old museum collections and covering how environmental changes impact little-known species. In addition to writing for <em>Hakai Magazine</em>, he has written for the<em> New York Times</em>, <em>Scientific American</em>, <em>National Geographic</em>, and other publications.</p></div>
